@startuml
title Telegram-бот регистрации визита в Qmatic Orchestra 6 — сетевой контур

!include style.iuml
skinparam BackgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor #f8fbff
  BorderColor #5b8cc0
}

actor "Посетитель\nTelegram-клиент" as Visitor

cloud "Интернет" as Internet {
  component "Telegram Bot API\napi.telegram.org:443" as TelegramApi
}

node "Корпоративный / филиальный контур" as Corp {
  node "DMZ / integration segment" as DMZ {
    component "Telegram Orchestra Bot\nPython + aiogram\npolling + CometD client" as Bot
  }

  node "Application segment" as App {
    component "Qmatic Orchestra 6" as Orchestra
    database "Orchestra DB" as OrchestraDb
  }

  component "DNS" as DNS
  component "NTP" as NTP
  component "Log collector\nstdout / journald / ELK" as Logs
}

Visitor --> TelegramApi : сообщения боту
Bot --> TelegramApi : HTTPS 443\ngetUpdates/sendMessage\nисходящее соединение

Bot --> Orchestra : REST API\nGET services\nPOST visits
Bot --> Orchestra : CometD /cometd\nhandshake/subscribe/connect\nlong-polling

Orchestra --> OrchestraDb : чтение/запись визитов
Bot --> DNS : DNS lookup
Bot --> NTP : time sync
Bot --> Logs : stdout logs

legend bottom center
|= № |= Соединение |
| 1 | Посетитель -> Telegram Bot API: сообщения боту |
| 2 | Bot -> Telegram Bot API: outbound HTTPS 443 (getUpdates/sendMessage) |
| 3 | Bot -> Orchestra REST API: GET services, POST visits |
| 4 | Bot -> Orchestra CometD: /cometd, handshake/subscribe/connect (long-polling) |
| 5 | Orchestra -> DB: чтение/запись визитов, услуги, VISIT_CALL |
| 6 | Bot -> DNS: разрешение имен |
| 7 | Bot -> NTP: синхронизация времени |
| 8 | Bot -> Log collector: stdout / journald / ELK |

Входящий порт из интернета не нужен:
бот работает через polling, а не через webhook.
endlegend

@enduml
